subject_information.comments: On some of the trials, the instruction was already written in the box and I couldn't change it. (I was the director.)  I could only hit "send".  I'm not sure if that's how things were supposed to work but I was surprised that for about half the trials I couldn't actually write what I wanted.
subject_information.strategy: I tried to describe the object as clearly as I could, making sure it was different from other objects I could see, and then give a clear instruction on where to move it.
